                  <handDesc hands="3">
                     <handNote script="textualisNorthern">All three scribes write <term type="script">gothic textura semiquadrata</term>, scribes 1 <locus from="1r" to="80r">(fols. 1–80)</locus> and 2 <locus from="81r" to="128r">(fols. 81–128)</locus> above top line, scribe 3 <locus from="129r" to="183r">(fols. 129–83)</locus> below it. Punctuation by <term type="punctuation">point</term>, <term type="punctuation">medial
